Adds a fully-connected Trending Products widget for the Recommendations team:

Atoms (shared primitives):
- Carousel — horizontal scrolling with arrow nav
- LoadingSkeleton — shimmer placeholder
- Popover — portal-based hover panel with SSR safety

Molecules:
- RecommendationsProductCard — product tile with image, title, price, favorite
- FavoriteButton — accessible aria-pressed toggle
- ProductCardPriceWithDetails — lazy-loaded price with Popover
- ProductCardPriceDetailsContent — price breakdown table
- ProductsCarouselWidget — carousel of product cards

API layer (reco/api/):
- mapper, types, imageUtils, mocks

Hooks:
- useTrendingProductsByCategory — SWR-based data fetching
